<h2 id=3D"MacOSSetup-PreSetup">Pre Setup</h2>
<p>Follow the following guides:</p>
<ol>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);"><a href=3D"/download/attachments/=
1125779143/1.%20Setting%20up%20your%20new%20Mac%20instructions.pdf?version=
=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1652677202560&amp;api=3Dv2" data-linked-resourc=
